oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 1939 article on Highlander from Vassar Review
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A 1939 article in the Vassar Review on Highlander Folk School, by Jane Lawson. Oddly the introduction lists the Vassar professor who donated the land to start Highlander as Dr. William Wyckoff Johnson, when it was Dr. Lillian Wyckoff Johnson.
